  "section_path": "Installation > Bootstrap > DNS validation",
  "page_start": 12,
  "page_end": 13,
  "chunk_ordinal": 1,
  "chunk_text": "Before starting the SNO bootstrap process, verify that the DNS records are correctly configured. The installation program requires that api.<cluster_name>.<base_domain> resolves to the bootstrap IP address and that *.apps.<cluster_name>.<base_domain> resolves to the node IP address. Use the dig command to verify DNS resolution before running the installation.",
